# Project Structure

This rule defines the organization and structure of the Axori monorepo.

## Monorepo Structure

```
axori/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/          # TanStack Start web app
│   ├── mobile/       # React Native/Expo app
│   └── api/          # Backend API (Hono)
├── packages/
│   ├── shared/       # Shared utilities, types, integrations
│   ├── db/           # Drizzle schema and migrations
│   └── ui/           # Design system components
```

## Component Placement Rules

### Reusable Components
- **Location**: `packages/ui/src/components/ComponentName.tsx`
- **Export**: Must export from `packages/ui/src/index.ts`
- **Usage**: Use across web and mobile apps
- **When**: Components used in multiple places or part of design system

### Page-Specific Components
- **Location**: `apps/web/src/components/ComponentName.tsx`
- **Usage**: Import directly in routes
- **When**: Components specific to web app pages

### Full Pages/Routes
- **Location**: `apps/web/src/routes/page-name.tsx`
- **Routing**: Follow TanStack Router file-based routing
- **When**: Complete page components

## Import Patterns

### Import Order
1. External dependencies (React, third-party libraries)
2. Internal packages (`@axori/db`, `@axori/shared`, `@axori/ui`)
3. Local imports (relative paths)

### Package Imports
```typescript
// ✅ Correct - Use package names
import { db } from "@axori/db";
import { Button } from "@axori/ui";
import { propertyInsertSchema } from "@axori/shared";

// ❌ Incorrect - Don't use relative paths across packages
import { db } from "../../../packages/db/src/client";
```

## Package Management

- **Package Manager**: pnpm (version >= 8.0.0)
- **Workspace**: Defined in `pnpm-workspace.yaml`
- **Build System**: Turborepo
- **Filtering**: Use `--filter` for package-specific commands

